---

<section class="what" id="what-this-is">
  <div class="what-inner">
    <div class="what-text">
      <span class="eyebrow">What This Is and Why It Exists</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The Problem This System Solves</h2>
      <p>
        Proactive Pixels runs a lead generation system where local service
        business owners fill out a form on a landing page, then call a shared
        Retell AI phone number to speak with an AI agent named Alex. The goal
        is for Alex to sound like he already knows who the caller is and what
        industry they're in, because he does.
      </p>
      <p>
        The problem: Retell doesn't know who's calling. It just sees an
        inbound phone number. This system bridges that gap by looking up the
        caller's information before the call connects, then telling Retell
        which specialized agent to use and what to call the person by name.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="what-callout">
      <div class="callout-card">
        <div class="callout-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 01-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 014.11 2h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.13 1.04.38 2.05.72 3.02a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.06-1.06a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.97.34 1.98.59 3.02.72A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Retell sees a phone number.</h3>
        <p>That's it. No name. No industry. No context.</p>
        <div class="callout-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="callout-icon callout-icon--blue">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
            <path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>This system looks it up.</h3>
        <p>Name, niche, and the right agent — returned in under a second.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 96px 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .what-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.73rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .what-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .what-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* Callout card */
  .callout-card {
    background: var(--light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .callout-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(27,58,110,0.08);
    color: var(--navy);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .callout-icon--blue {
    background: rgba(33,120,180,0.1);
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .callout-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .callout-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .callout-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--sky);
    margin: 1.25rem 0;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .what-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .what { padding: 64px 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
